 to reevangelize a decadent rome this captivating film highlights neris great love for youth his warm sense of humor contagious joy deep mystical spirituality and his amazing gift for miracles actor gigi proietti gives a moving performance as st philip in this beautifully produced film that is directed by giacomo campiotti director of the acclaimed films bakhita from slave to saint and st giuseppe moscatti includes a  page booklet also includes bonus features of the making of and behind the scenes  this dvd contains the following language options italian with english or spanish subtitles this is a region  dvd playable only in bermuda canada the cayman islands united states and us territories sample images from the film customers who bought this item also bought restless heart this dvd can only be sold in the us and canadaa special dvd collectors edition of the acclaimed epic film on st augustine of hippo filmed in europe the first fulllength feature movie on augus  dvd ignatius of loyola this dvd can only be sold in the us and canadathis modern and very human take on the story of st ignatius of loyola the founder of the jesuits often called the saint of second chances is an inc  dvd st teresa of avila this dvd can only be sold in the us canada and puerto rico a powerful epic miniseries shot on location in spain that tells the story of one of the most amazing women in history st teresa of avil  dvd bernadette this dvd is available for sale in us and canada only widescreen edition with many special features from jean delannoy one of france’s foremost filmmakers comes this top quality feature film produ  dvd saint peter this dvd can only be sold in the us and canadasaint peter tells the epic story about the key event in european and world history the spread of christianity throughout the roman empire focusing on   dvd you may also be interested in saint philip of the joyous heart   paperback ignatius of loyola   dvd get weekly specials your email here info  about us hi