ch on the back to allow for easy hanging on any wall at home or in the office this plaque – conceived and realized by a bronzesmith of world renown in germany – is a great gift for that special “philip” in your life saint of joy saint of humor saint philip neri one of the patron saints of rome was during his lifetime a true sign of contradiction immersed in the postrenaissance malaise of his time ad living in a corrupt rome filled with apathetic clergy he pursued a life of piety combined with playful humor and a shrewd wit st philip considered a cheerful temperament more a mark of christians than a melancholy one  for him “a joyful heart is more easily made perfect than a downcast one” reviewsthere are no reviews yetwould you like to submit yours be the first to review “saint philip neri plaque” cancel replyyou must be logged in to post a comment additional information weight  lbs dimensions  x  x  in related products st francis of assisi with animals plaque  add to cart details compare share share on facebook twitter google pinterest solid bronze wall plaque x  inchesmade in germanygift box included details saint christopher car plaque  add to cart details compare share share on facebook twitter google pinterest solid bronze with adhesive backing inchesmade in germanygift box included details magnetic saint christopher car plaque  add to cart details compare share share on facebook twitter google pinterest solid bronze plaque with magnet inches in diametermade in germanygift box included details catholic  anglican  baptist  ecumenical  episcopal  lutheran  methodist  presbyterian  mennonite  evangelical  nondenominational  quaker  pentecostal stay in contact sign up for our email promotions get to know usabout us our story fundraising news reviews blog featured items submit a photo new items contact us customer serviceshipping  returns on sale login  register faq track package change address special accountsnonprofit sign up wholesale sign up nonprofit login wholes